install with:

git clone [url] ~/.vim

ln -nfs ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -nfs ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
-------------------------------

build:

either get from vim.org and install with hg
or download from my vim mirror on github with

git clone git://github.com/johnantoni/vim.git
cd vim/src
./configure --with-features=huge --enable-rubyinterp
make && sudo make install

if you encounter an error on build, run the command
below before you re-configure & build:

make distclean


